---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Watch Repair Specialists">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">About Us</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p>
        Welcome to Watch Repair Specialists, your dedicated resource for finding expert watch repair services.
        Our mission is to connect watch owners with skilled and reliable watchmakers across the country,
        making the process of maintaining and repairing your cherished timepieces as easy and stress-free as possible.
      </p>
      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>
        Founded by a team of passionate horologists, Watch Repair Specialists was born out of a desire to create a trusted,
        centralized platform for watch enthusiasts. We saw a need for a reliable resource that not only lists repair shops
        but also provides valuable insights into the quality and specialization of each. Our founders, with over 20 years of
        combined experience in the watch industry, have meticulously curated this directory to ensure every listing meets our
        high standards of excellence.
      </p>
      <h2>Our Commitment to Quality</h2>
      <p>
        We understand the value, both sentimental and monetary, that a watch can hold.
        That's why we've built a comprehensive directory designed to help you quickly locate professionals
        who specialize in everything from routine battery replacements and strap adjustments to complex
        movement overhauls and vintage watch restorations. Each specialist in our network is vetted for their
        expertise, customer service, and reliability.
      </p>
      <h2>Why Trust Us?</h2>
      <p>
        Our platform is built on the principles of Experience, Expertise, Authoritativeness, and Trust (E-E-A-T).
        We strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information, ensuring you can make informed decisions
        when choosing a watch repair specialist. Whether you're a seasoned collector or a first-time watch owner,
        we're here to support your watch care journey with transparent reviews and detailed service information.
      </p>
      <p>
        Thank you for choosing Watch Repair Specialists. We look forward to helping you keep your timepieces ticking perfectly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
